02:14.198 --> 02:19.584
Another 40 years passed in triumph and sorrow and bloodshed and blessing.

02:19.604 --> 02:23.509
Promises whispered in the shadows bound the people to something eternal.

02:24.650 --> 02:30.317
Through profit, king, and covenant, the story moved forward toward a light not yet seen.

02:30.738 --> 02:34.322
Three generations closer to an ancient promise on the way.

02:34.626 --> 02:48.279
for man and kings and prophets alike, the story unfolds, a glimpse of what's to come, a greater king who will reign forever, fulfilling the promise, redeeming the world through the ultimate sacrifice.

02:59.490 --> 03:00.531
I promise.

03:02.513 --> 03:03.634
Have you ever said those words?

03:05.250 --> 03:06.151
