40:02.712 --> 40:08.722
And it says, thus says, the Lord refrain your voice from weeping, that your children will come back from the land of the enemy.

40:09.602 --> 40:17.610
And that is an amazing statement to give to me, opening the world, and yet it was specifically for me.

40:17.990 --> 40:25.217
I don't have to cry anymore, I don't have to worry anymore, I don't have to speak sad words anymore, because Chris is coming back from the land of the enemy.

40:25.938 --> 40:26.819
It's an amazing thing.

40:27.840 --> 40:34.987
So my wife and I, in high school, we were friends, but during this time, her and I became more than friends.

40:35.467 --> 40:38.130
Very toxic relationship, we don't know Jesus.

40:38.530 --> 40:42.995
And so we ended up breaking up, which was almost another traumatic experience for me.

40:43.015 --> 40:50.784
But when I come to know Jesus, and I give my life to Him, somehow, someway, we get reconnected.

40:50.965 --> 40:53.107
So I start to tell her about my relationship with Jesus.

40:53.367 --> 40:55.310
She's kind of exploring some other things.

40:55.570 --> 40:57.793
She's just coming off a broken relationship.

40:58.353 --> 41:05.682
And then we start to reconnect, and I start to invite her to church, and she starts coming, and eventually she gives her life to Jesus.

41:06.082 --> 41:11.148
Our relationship starts to be rebuilt slowly, but there's a lot of hurt and brokenness there, so it takes a while.

41:11.709 --> 41:22.842
But eventually, I work up the nerve to propose, and we get married, and we're now a blended family, which is part of my story that is very similar, because I was part of the blended family.

41:22.862 --> 41:24.584
And we started off with Savannah.

41:24.665 --> 41:29.170
She was about three years old when we got married, and it was cool to just

41:29.826 --> 41:37.178
See the example that Tom and the way that he loved me and cared for me is the same thing I now get to do for Savannah.

41:37.198 --> 41:38.961
And the Lord has been so good to our family.

41:39.301 --> 41:40.523
You know, we have three amazing kids.

41:40.723 --> 41:41.665
Savannah is our oldest.

41:41.825 --> 41:44.149
Elijah is our middle and Jacob's our youngest.

41:45.892 --> 41:57.490
I think if I was able to talk to the old me, I would try to help him to see that the things of this world are fading, that there is something beyond this world and those things don't last forever.

41:57.762 --> 42:05.212
And you know, I say that church almost every single time I'm doing an altar call, that my one regret as a Christian is that I didn't give my life to Jesus sooner.

42:05.472 --> 42:08.456
And when I think about all the years that I raised it, they're suing the things of the world.

42:09.117 --> 42:14.525
And now all the hurt and the scars I carry from that, like he's redeemed that, but there's still scars.

42:15.226 --> 42:24.338
And if I could just go back in time and give my life to him like so much earlier, those would be some of the things I think I would say to a younger me.

42:31.746 --> 42:38.272
Our God is faithful for a thousand generations.

42:38.312 --> 42:54.007
Listen, if you're a mom or dad or grandma or grandpa and you have a prodigal son or prodigal dog, don't stop praying, don't stop pleading, don't stop begging, don't stop knocking on heaven's door because God wants to reach out to those who are far from him and he wants to use your prayers as a catalyst.

42:55.429 --> 42:56.129
You see, it's crazy.

42:56.149 --> 42:57.891
God didn't just want to save Chris.

42:59.412 --> 43:01.074
He wanted to use Chris to reach others.

43:02.146 --> 43:03.908
God didn't just want to bless Hannah's prayer.

43:04.188 --> 43:06.791
No, Sam would bless generations of people.

43:06.811 --> 43:08.113
And this is what God loves to do.

43:08.153 --> 43:12.477
He still saves and delivers and heals, but he wants to use our life to go after the one.

43:13.719 --> 43:20.286
And so I want us to just take a moment of reflecting on the goodness and the goodness and power of God that we see in Hannah's song that he is king over the university.

43:20.306 --> 43:21.247
He made everything.

43:22.148 --> 43:27.634
And if you've lost your awe at the bigness of God, if your head is buried in all the

43:27.778 --> 43:31.343
Broken news of the world, and you haven't seen the beauty and power of God's creation.

43:31.364 --> 43:34.388
Every morning, creation worships God.

43:35.670 --> 43:38.515
And we hope this song brings you back to that sense of all.

43:38.575 --> 43:45.545
And if you feel lost in the bigness of the world, like God doesn't see you, this is a reminder, like in Hannah's song.

43:46.206 --> 43:56.402
He sees you, he knows you, and he has a way to go after the one in a way that you will never understand the mystery of his pursuit and love for us.

43:56.738 --> 43:58.283
is beyond imagination.

43:58.343 --> 44:00.751
So this song is called, So Will I.

44:01.513 --> 44:08.135
And may this meditation fill our hearts and minds with awe and cause us to worship Him anew.

44:09.098 --> 44:09.780
Here's the song.

44:10.061 --> 44:10.482
So will I.

51:17.602 --> 51:26.574
This is why we praise Him, a God who is faithful for a thousand generations, and that faithfulness has come to us, and that's why we worship.

51:27.875 --> 51:36.206
But I know there's probably some people in this room that maybe you've been curious about God, or maybe even you believe in God, but you've never bowed your knee to God.

51:36.226 --> 51:40.932
You've never said, God, I wanna make it my chief goal in life to honor you above all else.

51:41.873 --> 51:45.458
I wanna believe the gospel that my sins can be forgiven, like Chris,

51:45.698 --> 51:49.783
far away from God, but the prayers of his mom reached heaven.

51:50.724 --> 51:56.651
Listen, I'm standing here because the prayers of my mom and dad and my grandma and grandpa reached heaven.

51:57.712 --> 52:01.837
I was on a course to destruction and God came after me.

52:03.579 --> 52:06.843
The God of the universe comes after the one.

52:06.903 --> 52:13.170
And if you're that one person here far from God, we want to create this moment to give you a chance to respond.

52:14.498 --> 52:24.914
A thousand generations of God's love and faithfulness to those who will come, those who will believe, those who will submit their lives to who he is.

52:24.974 --> 52:29.942
This is why Jesus came to build a way back to God, to die on a cross, to pay your sin debt.

52:31.545 --> 52:39.377
Today, I want you to know this, this world you live in is not an accident, and you are not an accident, and this moment is not a coincidence.

52:41.640 --> 52:42.802
Everything in your life

52:43.714 --> 52:52.626
God is creating to make you look maybe for the first time at him, because he is the missing piece of your life.

52:52.666 --> 52:57.392
You were created for a relationship with a living God, but he doesn't force it on you.

52:58.273 --> 52:59.254
He invites you to it.

53:00.055 --> 53:07.285
Whoever is willing to come, whoever repents, whoever believes, they can be forgiven, they can be saved.

53:08.506 --> 53:09.468
And so we're going to invite you.

53:09.628 --> 53:11.250
You're already standing, step into the aisle.

53:12.002 --> 53:14.085
Walk this way, say a prayer of faith.

53:14.366 --> 53:17.591
We're gonna sing this song called Reckless Love, How God Pursues Us.

53:17.891 --> 53:18.612
And here's what I know.

53:18.672 --> 53:23.119
When you step into the aisle, this place will break into applause because we know what this meant for us when we did it.

53:23.360 --> 53:27.146
And we can't wait to see heaven full because we've been praying for you.

53:27.526 --> 53:34.437
If that's you right now, take that step into the aisle and walk this way and God will bless your life in a measurable ways.

53:34.477 --> 53:35.058
Come on.

54:37.794 --> 54:45.852
So we celebrate these decisions and we are so grateful that we get to be a part of this moment where you can meet Jesus, where your sins can be forgiven.

54:45.912 --> 54:47.576
Here's the craziness.

54:47.596 --> 54:49.660
Your whole life, your sin is separated you from God.

54:49.700 --> 54:54.591
But now he's going to separate sin from you as far as the east is from the west as you make this confession.

54:54.651 --> 54:57.618
His grace is going to meet you in this moment.

54:59.042 --> 55:01.466
Here's the promise of God, and God always keeps His promise.

55:01.606 --> 55:03.309
I will wash away your sin.

55:03.369 --> 55:05.592
I will write your name in my book of life.

55:05.973 --> 55:10.841
This is the most important place your name will ever be written, because that means your destination is heaven.

55:10.861 --> 55:16.610
That means you are now a son or daughter of Jesus, and no one's going to snatch you out of the hand of God.

55:16.650 --> 55:21.618
It is strong enough to hold you, and we are grateful to be a part of this moment.

55:23.554 --> 55:29.584
And so in a moment, we're going to pray a prayer with you and lead you in this prayer, but I just want to offer one more encouragement.

55:31.707 --> 55:33.971
Chris said, at the greatest regret he had it, he didn't do it sooner.

55:34.252 --> 55:35.193
That's my greatest regret.

55:36.075 --> 55:40.262
For so long, I wrestle with doubts and fears and questions that wanted to be in control and live my own life.

55:42.585 --> 55:43.627
And I wasted a lot of time.

55:46.572 --> 55:50.258
But there are certain moments that can change your whole life.

55:50.402 --> 55:52.044
Not every moment in life is created equal.

55:52.064 --> 55:54.307
And sometimes there's a weight of a moment that you feel.

55:54.368 --> 56:00.056
It's you just know, like, I need to do something different.

56:00.076 --> 56:03.440
And if you've never tried Jesus, he'd never given your life completely to him.

56:03.500 --> 56:10.811
Listen, he's been waiting and people around you have been praying because they love you.

56:12.273 --> 56:13.514
God doesn't just want to save you.

56:14.416 --> 56:15.758
He wants to give you a purpose.

56:16.959 --> 56:18.962
