56:20.066 --> 56:24.533
And so, if that's you, we call this 20 seconds of insane courage.

56:25.855 --> 56:32.264
Step into the aisle in front of all these people and walk forward and watch God receive you as a son, as a daughter.

56:32.685 --> 56:33.967
Watch him do a miracle in your life.

56:34.007 --> 56:35.269
If that's you, we're not gonna play another line.

56:35.289 --> 56:37.692
Just step into the aisle and walk this way.

56:37.993 --> 56:38.994
Come on, come on.

56:48.962 --> 56:49.443
So good.

56:49.543 --> 56:50.024
So good.

56:50.464 --> 56:50.705
Come on.

56:56.974 --> 56:59.418
If you're in the back or you're in the middle, people will move for you.

56:59.438 --> 56:59.899
Trust me.

57:01.501 --> 57:03.945
This is the miracle moment right here.

57:03.965 --> 57:05.448
This is God going after people.

57:10.175 --> 57:10.395
All right.

57:12.559 --> 57:17.426
This is why Jesus came to seek and save the loss, to fill heaven.

57:20.450 --> 57:33.803
So today, come on, we see people who are willing and ready to give their whole life to the only one who is worthy of our life, the only one who never breaks his promise.

57:37.366 --> 57:38.847
And so here is the promise of God.

57:40.048 --> 57:45.654
If you confess your sin, he is faithful and just to forgive you every sin and cleanse you from unrighteousness.

57:45.814 --> 57:47.676
Today God is gonna keep that promise in your life.

57:49.357 --> 57:50.258
Come on, come on.

57:55.842 --> 57:56.783
I'm so glad you're here.

58:01.488 --> 58:02.609
I don't want moments like this to end.

58:02.629 --> 58:04.511
This is like such a great moment.

58:07.354 --> 58:09.016
All these prayers that people prayed for you.

58:10.998 --> 58:11.979
God is answering right now.

58:13.120 --> 58:13.921
Because He's faithful.

58:15.162 --> 58:15.823
Even when we're not.

58:17.245 --> 58:18.866
And so I'm gonna give you some words to say to God.

58:20.608 --> 58:21.189
He knows you.

58:21.329 --> 58:22.450
He knows everything about you.

58:23.458 --> 58:26.943
And as you pray this prayer sincerely, as you confess you're a sinner, that you need to save you.

58:28.225 --> 58:31.830
As you thank Jesus for coming to die in your place, and now you're gonna live for Him.

58:33.112 --> 58:36.898
And that prayer of confession is just the beginning of the great adventure of following Jesus.

58:37.078 --> 58:39.441
And so, save this to God, He's listening.

58:40.122 --> 58:40.743
Save this out loud.

58:40.823 --> 58:45.651
Lord God, I open my heart and I invite you inside.

58:47.073 --> 58:48.014
Forgive my sin.

58:48.094 --> 58:50.738
Today I repent.

58:51.874 --> 58:58.365
Now, fill me with your spirit, and I will walk with you all the days of my life.

58:59.507 --> 59:00.849
I pray this in Jesus' name.

59:02.712 --> 59:03.474
Amen.

59:03.494 --> 59:03.894
Amen.

59:03.935 --> 59:05.637
Guys, congratulations.

59:05.657 --> 59:06.940
We are so excited for you.

59:07.901 --> 59:10.706
So listen, before you go back to your seats.

59:11.170 --> 59:13.355
